PluginData.Author: Blues Hailfire
PluginData.Tooltip: Changes the default jump effect to one inspired by the Dune Series
PluginData.Description: Space folding (Dune), the specific portrayal of faster-than-light travel in Frank Herbert's Dune series. Space curvature due to gravity, a central aspect of the general theory of relativity. Space-time folding, a physical concept of non-flat spacetime, related to wormholes.
